  "title": "Torchier Torches",
  "description": "Gives all the torches in the game the new Redstone Torch outline from Snapshot 24w33a.",
  "body": "---\n<p align=\"center\"?>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/torchier-torches\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bf84aa11b4afd69cdbd20a199bc6d93c50fac58b.png\" \n        alt=\"Modrinth\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/torchier-torches\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3531508338997863e0b15c2252d16bf51ceb5669.png\" \n        alt=\"Curseforge\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/torchier-torches/\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eac8caa46edda35d821be9a2e1a8e16a00a9cadc.png\" \n        alt=\"Planet Minecraft\" \n        width=\"64\"  \n        style=\"display: block; margin: 0 auto\" /></a>\n</p>  \n\n---\n\n**Torchier Torches** is a simple resource pack that adds an outline around the torches in the game. This effect is achieved by giving the outline cubes negative sizes so that they render underneath the base torch model.\n\n![Torch](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/beuIkbn5/images/811453f33a5af944a69fad233a56d17b4cfa004b.png)\n![Redstone Torch](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/beuIkbn5/images/6dd0f65001c877142040ad5d6c6adf5bb08faeab.png)\n![Soul Torch](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/beuIkbn5/images/96325f122a748ba20f240f5eed4e3aca0d85b1f8.png)\n\n---\n",
